Description
-----------

This CVar allows the engine to use an alternative method for skinning
that shifts more work to the GPU.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    r_useNewSkinning [Boolean]

Parameters
----------

-   [Boolean]
    -   0 - Disable.
    -   1 - Enable.

