Notes
-----

This CVar should only be enabled when used with [DX9
class](Vertex_and_fragment_programs "Vertex and fragment programs")
video cards. Even so it might be advantageous to disable this CVar if
your video card is low-end and/or if you have a very fast CPU in which
case the original method might still prove to be faster.

